**Special Containment Procedures:** An indeterminate number of [OBJECT] instances are to be held in [[[https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/scp-5310 |Special Special Containers]]] in Site-⌘. As for uncontained instances of [OBJECT], I wouldn't worry about it much. After all, Foundation disinformation authorities are to inform the public that the purpose of [OBJECT]s is unclear, despite the fact that they are obviously meant for [INTENDED PURPOSE]. //Obviously//. 

At request of the Department of Surrealistics, [OBJECT] has been reclassified to Thaumiel as of last Thursday. Instances are to be used for [INTENDED PURPOSE] by Site-⌘ staff whenever necessary.

@@ @@

